name: IGC Monogram Snapback
description:
It's red and white and its got our IGC monogram badge on it, what else is there to know? Ohh its a snapback and its freaking awesome! We've been talking about this hat for ages and now its finally here!

Buy one now!!!! Postage is just £1 to everywhere! UK, USA, Tahiti... Everywhere! 

Pick one up now and we'll send you an ink beermat!

name: INK IV - Rad to the Power of Sick
description:
INK IV should be hitting shops this month, but we've got a few extra T's in the stock room that we can sell on our store in advance.. want to pick up a T from our new range before they hit shops, buy one today!

This is our 'rad to the power of sick' design, large print on the front of the T with INK badge at the bottom and INK IV neck print.
